{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/rayokota/awesome-hbase/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c1ddd7e4-ddd8-59ac-9797-856953218740","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-hbase-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-hbase-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome hbase awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome HBase <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"http://hbase.apache.org/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/rayokota/awesome-hbase/c197f415/hbase_logo_with_orca-2.png\" align=\"right\" width=\"150\"></a></p>\n<p>A curated list of awesome HBase projects and resources.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hbase.apache.org\">HBase</a> is a distributed, scalable, big data store.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#projects\">Projects</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#clients\">Clients</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cloud\">Cloud</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#frameworks\">Frameworks</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#datasets\">Datasets</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#document\">Document</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#entityjpa\">Entity/JPA</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#geospatial\">Geospatial</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#graph\">Graph</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sqlolap\">SQL/OLAP</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#time-series\">Time Series</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#infrastructure\">Infrastructure</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#secondary-indices\">Secondary Indices</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#transactions\">Transactions</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#integrations\">Integrations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#miscellaneous\">Miscellaneous</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#resources\">Resources</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#books\">Books</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#papers\">Papers</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"projects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#projects\" aria-label=\"projects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Projects</h2>\n<h3 id=\"clients\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clients\" aria-label=\"clients permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Clients</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/OpenTSDB/asynchbase\">asynchbase</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/OpenTSDB/asynchbase\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">595</span></span></a> - Fully asynchronous, non-blocking HBase client.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tsuna/gohbase\">gohbase</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tsuna/gohbase\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">559</span></span></a> - Pure Go client for HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wbolster/happybase\">happybase</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wbolster/happybase\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">562</span></span></a> - Python client for HBase.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"cloud\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cloud\" aria-label=\"cloud permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cloud</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/emr/\">Amazon EMR</a> - Amazon's Hadoop/HBase offering on AWS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/hdinsight/\">Azure HDInsight</a> - Microsoft's Hadoop/HBase offering on Azure.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cloudera.com/products/product-components/cloudera-director.html\">Cloudera Director</a> - Run Hadoop/HBase clusters on AWS, Azure or Google Cloud.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/bigtable/\">Google Cloud Bigtable</a> - High-performance NoSQL database service accessible via HBase client API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hortonworks.com/open-source/cloudbreak/\">Hortonworks Cloudbreak</a> - Provision Hadoop/HBase clusters on AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, or OpenStack.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"frameworks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#frameworks\" aria-label=\"frameworks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Frameworks</h3>\n<h4 id=\"datasets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#datasets\" aria-label=\"datasets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Datasets</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://kitesdk.org\">Kite</a> - High-level data layer for Hadoop/HBase.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"document\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#document\" aria-label=\"document permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Document</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rayokota/hdocdb\">HDocDB</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rayokota/hdocdb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">24</span></span></a> - HBase as a JSON document database.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"entityjpa\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#entityjpa\" aria-label=\"entityjpa permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Entity/JPA</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.datanucleus.org\">DataNucleus</a> - JPA persistence layer with support for HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://gora.apache.org\">Gora</a> - Persistence library for big data with support for HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rayokota/hentitydb\">HEntityDB</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rayokota/hentitydb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - HBase as an entity database.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/impetus-opensource/Kundera\">Kundera</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/impetus-opensource/Kundera\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">893</span></span></a> - JPA client with support for HBase.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"geospatial\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#geospatial\" aria-label=\"geospatial permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Geospatial</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.geomesa.org/\">GeoMesa</a> - Spatial-temporal database with support for Accumulo, HBase, Cassandra, and Kafka.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"graph\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#graph\" aria-label=\"graph permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Graph</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dbs-leipzig/gradoop\">Gradoop</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dbs-leipzig/gradoop\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">200</span></span></a> - Research framework for scalable graph analytics built on Flink and HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rayokota/hgraphdb\">HGraphDB</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rayokota/hgraphdb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">228</span></span></a> - HBase as a TinkerPop graph database.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://janusgraph.org/\">JanusGraph</a> - Scalable graph database with support for Cassandra, HBase, Google Cloud Bigtable, and BerkeleyDB.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula\">NebulaGraph</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6.2k</span></span></a> - A high performance distributed Graph database.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://s2graph.incubator.apache.org\">S2Graph</a> - High-performance distributed graph database built on HBase.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"sqlolap\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sqlolap\" aria-label=\"sqlolap permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SQL/OLAP</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://antsdb.com/\">AntsDB</a> - AntsDB is a low latency, high concurrency, MySQL compliant SQL layer for HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://esgyn.com/\">EsgynDB</a> - Commercial SQL engine providing ACID transactions and BI analytics on top of Hadoop, based on Trafodian.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://kylin.apache.org\">Kylin</a> - Extreme OLAP engine for big data that stores data in HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.leanxcale.com\">LeanXScale</a> - Commercial full ACID full SQL product built on Hadoop/HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://phoenix.apache.org\">Phoenix</a> - SQL layer on top of HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.splicemachine.com\">Splice Machine</a> - Commercial RDBMS built on top of HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://trafodion.apache.org\">Trafodian</a> - Transactional SQL-on-Hadoop/HBase.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"time-series\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#time-series\" aria-label=\"time series permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Time Series</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://axibase.com/products/axibase-time-series-database/\">Axibase</a> - Distributed time series database built on HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://opentsdb.net\">OpenTSDB</a> - Scalable time series database built on HBase.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.warp10.io\">Warp 10</a> - Time series database for sensor data.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"infrastructure\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#infrastructure\" aria-label=\"infrastructure permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Infrastructure</h3>\n<h4 id=\"secondary-indices\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#secondary-indices\" aria-label=\"secondary indices permali